description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from "CHRONO CIRCLE" and "Tetote Connect"!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Skyfall / PIKASONIC & Tatsunoshin
・PAPAN! Very Love! / Shinra-Bansho
・SUPER☆HARAGURO☆POP / Zekk
・SKYDAZE / HyuN
・A Tetocone With You /　MASAKI(ZUNTATA)×Dorothy(CV:Inori Minase)
・Beniiro Parasol feat. Yukacco / REDALiCE
・FURETE-MITAI / Mikito P
・Tetote Awasete / Coteani＆Yu Shimoda (ZUNTATA)
・edge//lord / NAOKI feat. Riyu Kosaka
・???(Secret)

■Navigator
Verdi(CV: Nanahira) *with voice
Dorothy(CV: Inori Minase) *with voice

■Avatar
・VERDI(2D)
・DOROTHY(2D)
・PATTIE(2D)
・FIER(2D)
・GOARE(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: CHRONO CIRCLE + Tetote Connect Pack
